sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"java plain\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace !important; min-height: auto !important;\">root /usr/share/nginx/html; # 静态文件路径</code></div>\r\n							<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\" style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; border-radius: 0px !important; background: none rgb(244, 244, 244) !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important;\">\r\n								<code class=\"java spaces\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace !important; min-height: auto !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"java plain\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace !important; min-height: auto !important;\">}</code></div>\r\n							<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\" style=\"margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; border-radius: 0px !important; background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important;\">\r\n								<code class=\"java plain\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace !important; min-height: auto !important;\">}</code></div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n			</tbody>\r\n		</table>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	2、反向代理服务器</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	什么是反向代理？</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	客户端本来可以直接通过HTTP协议访问某网站应用服务器，网站管理员可以在中间加上一个Nginx，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	客户端请求Nginx，Nginx请求应用服务器，然后将结果返回给客户端，此时Nginx就是反向代理服务器。</p>\r\n', '2016-12-11 19:17', '3', '1', '3', '1', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('29', '5', '马士兵', '<div 12px=\"\" baike.bdimg.com=\"\" center=\"\" class=\"edit-prompt\" color:=\"\" editprompt=\"\" font-family:=\"\" http:=\"\" img=\"\" lemma_content=\"\" maincontent=\"\" no-repeat=\"\" static=\"\" style=\"clear: both; height: 37px; line-height: 37px; width: 755px; margin: 10px 0px; padding-left: 35px; background: url(\" widget=\"\" wiki-lemma=\"\">\r\n	本词条缺少<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">名片图</span>，补充相关内容使词条更完整，还能快速升级，赶紧来<a class=\"edit-prompt-link j-edit-link\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); cursor: pointer;\">编辑</a>吧！</div>\r\n<div class=\"lemma-summary\" label-module=\"lemmaSummary\" style=\"clear: both; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">\r\n		马士兵是一名<a data-lemmaid=\"17058\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/subview/187895/6353038.htm\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">战士</a>，出生于新民乡能昌村。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"configModuleBanner\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div background-attachment:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" baike.bdimg.com=\"\" basicinfo=\"\" class=\"basic-info cmn-clearfix\" color:=\"\" font-family:=\"\" http:=\"\" img=\"\" lemma_content=\"\" maincontent=\"\" static=\"\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 35px; clear: both; background-image: url(\" widget=\"\" wiki-lemma=\"\">\r\n	<dl class=\"basicInfo-block basicInfo-left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 395px; float: left;\">\r\n		<dt class=\"basicInfo-item name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 12px; line-height: 26px; float: left; width: 90px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\r\n			中文名</dt>\r\n		<dd class=\"basicInfo-item value\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; float: left; zoom: 1; width: 285px; position: relative;\">\r\n			马士兵</dd>\r\n		<dt class=\"basicInfo-item name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 12px; line-height: 26px; float: left; width: 90px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\r\n			国&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;籍</dt>\r\n		<dd class=\"basicInfo-item value\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; float: left; zoom: 1; width: 285px; position: relative;\">\r\n			&nbsp;中国</dd>\r\n		<dt class=\"basicInfo-item name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 12px; line-height: 26px; float: left; width: 90px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\r\n			出生地</dt>\r\n		<dd class=\"basicInfo-item value\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; float: left; zoom: 1; width: 285px; position: relative;\">\r\n			新民乡能昌村</dd>\r\n	</dl>\r\n	<dl class=\"basicInfo-block basicInfo-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 395px; float: left;\">\r\n		<dt class=\"basicInfo-item name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 12px; line-height: 26px; float: left; width: 90px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\r\n			出生日期</dt>\r\n		<dd class=\"basicInfo-item value\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; float: left; zoom: 1; width: 285px; position: relative;\">\r\n			1926</dd>\r\n		<dt class=\"basicInfo-item name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 12px; line-height: 26px; float: left; width: 90px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\r\n			逝世日期</dt>\r\n		<dd class=\"basicInfo-item value\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; float: left; zoom: 1; width: 285px; position: relative;\">\r\n			1949年5月</dd>\r\n		<dt class=\"basicInfo-item name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 12px; line-height: 26px; float: left; width: 90px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\r\n			职&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;业</dt>\r\n		<dd class=\"basicInfo-item value\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; float: left; zoom: 1; width: 285px; position: relative;\">\r\n			战士</dd>\r\n		<dt class=\"basicInfo-item name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 12px; line-height: 26px; float: left; width: 90px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\r\n			性&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;别</dt>\r\n		<dd class=\"basicInfo-item value\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; float: left; zoom: 1; width: 285px; position: relative;\">\r\n			&nbsp;男</dd>\r\n	</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">牺牲</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n	1949年5月上海月浦战斗中牺牲。</div>\r\n<div id=\"open-tag\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 30px; border-top: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); overflow: hidden; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<div class=\"open-tag-title\" style=\"float: left; font-weight: 700; margin-right: 15px; height: 20px;\">\r\n		词条标签：</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"open-tag\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 30px; border-top: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); overflow: hidden; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<span class=\"taglist\">人物</span></div>\r\n', '2016-12-11 19:23', '2', '0', '3', '1', '3', '0');
