;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">分</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，<span style=\"color:red\">登录一次加</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">分</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">,</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">被评论加</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">分，被置顶加</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">10</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">分）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">3.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">规定帖子的阅读权限（比如游客不可看），规定评论权限（比如不可评论）；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: 21.1pt;\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">4..</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">当用户的帖子被别人评论时，即使通知该用户（类似于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">qq</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">的通知功能）。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">5. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">为版主提供帖子置顶功能；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">6.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">论坛包括多个版面，比如体育版，生活版，学习版等等，每个版有版主。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">7.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">模糊查询用户；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">8.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">根据标题或者内容，模糊查询帖子；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">9.</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;color:red\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">用户登录密码错了一次之后，下一次登录需要验证码校验码；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">11.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">超级管理员、版主后台发布公告；所有用户</span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">在版面最上看到跑马灯显示公告。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">12. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">发送邮件通知到用户注册邮箱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">HttpSessionBindingListener<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\">13. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:yellow\">实时在线用户数（包括登录用户和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\">guest</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:yellow\">游客（没有登录的访问用户））</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\">https://www.cnblogs.com/<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\">14. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:yellow\">实时登录用户数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\"> ,</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:yellow\">文章，评论，总注册人数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:yellow\">15.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:yellow\">粉丝，朋友圈</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:\r\nyellow\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '2016-12-11 22:47', '2', '0', '3', '1', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('34', '1', '《Web程序设计》期末考核', '<h2 style=\"line-height:200%\">\r\n	<a name=\"OLE_LINK1\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">考核时间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></a></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">周上课时间。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height:200%;tab-stops:114.8pt\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">考核方式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">考勤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，实验成绩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，期末考核</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">期末考核方式：完成系统，向老师演示，老师根据系统提出问题。根据系统功能和回答问题的好坏决定成绩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height:200%\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">完善论坛的功能</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">下列备选的功能，每个人选择完成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4-5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个小功能</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">比如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.a),2.b)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">之类的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，根据效果和回答老师提问，可以给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60-85</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分。之后多做功能，继续加分，直至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 39.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">用户管理模块：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">划分角色和权限：超级管理员（所有用户的管理：增加、删除、查询用户）；版主（可以删除本版的帖子）；普通用户（可以增删改自己发布的帖子，可以查看并评论所有帖子）；游客（可以查看所有帖子，不能评论）；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">经验值：根据登录次数、登录时长、发布帖子数量、评论帖子数量，给予经验值，并且根据经验值给出对应的职位或者称呼；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">通过邮箱注册，绑定邮箱的功能。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 39.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">发布帖子模块</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">发布帖子时候可以贴上图片、上传附件；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">规定帖子的阅读权限（比如游客不可看），规定评论权限（比如不可评论）；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">当用户的帖子被别人评论时，即使通知该用户（类似于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">qq</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的通知功能）；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为版主提供帖子置顶功能；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">论坛包括多个版面，比如体育版，生活版，学习版等等，每个版有版主。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso