quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">实时登录用户数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">记录网站的用户登录日志（登录，退出信息等）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 39.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">账号安全</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">用户登录密码错了一次之后，下一次登录需要验证码校验码；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">同个账号登录，密码错误</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">次后，锁死账号。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（可以是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">小时后解锁，或者通过注册邮箱发送链接解锁）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">同个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">地址尝试各种账号，密码登录错误</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">次之后，锁死</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">地址，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">小时后解封。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 39.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">系统公告功能模块</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">超级管理员、版主后台发布公告；所有用户</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在版面最上看到跑马灯显示公告。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 39.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">站内邮件功能模块</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">站内用户可以互发邮件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 63.0pt\">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">发送邮件通知到用户注册邮箱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height:200%\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">组队完成一个系统</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一个组最多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个人，要求分工明确，每个人完成一个模块，比如：用户管理模块、基础数据管理模块、查询统计模块等等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '2016-12-11 22:48', '15', '2', '3', '1', '1', '0');
